## Key Insights
- Game has massive internal randomness: same code, same seed → 0.00 or 19.19
- Economy protection helps but can't fully prevent wipeouts (stochastic)
- Heart supply-gated batching seems to help (more hearts per trip)
- 2 scramblers better than 1, but 3rd aligner better than 3rd scrambler
- 2 miners is the sweet spot for late game
- Focus should be on maximizing upside (more >10 games) rather than preventing all wipeouts
